2
00:00:06,430 --> 00:00:09,480
Unexpectedly, there's someone between us.

3
00:00:09,480 --> 00:00:12,559
♫ This journey is full of obstacles ♫

4
00:00:12,559 --> 00:00:16,649
I suddenly feel very distant.

5
00:00:16,649 --> 00:00:18,340
♫ Lifting our heads up suddenly ♫

6
00:00:18,340 --> 00:00:21,059
- Hi.
- I can finally see you.

7
00:00:21,060 --> 00:00:24,140
♫ Show me. Show me. Your eyes ♫

8
00:00:25,039 --> 00:00:29,169
♫ One step, two steps. I'm in a daze and don't understand easily ♫

9
00:00:29,169 --> 00:00:33,439
♫ Clearing my head, I realize who doesn't
care about the rights and wrongs ♫

10
00:00:33,439 --> 00:00:36,389
♫ Hey, our last playing cards are on the table ♫

11
00:00:36,389 --> 00:00:38,539
♫ Hurry up and write down your promise ♫

12
00:00:38,540 --> 00:00:41,030
♫ Don't change it ♫

13
00:00:41,030 --> 00:00:45,129
♫ In the next moment, tears are falling in the wind like drizzle ♫

14
00:00:45,129 --> 00:00:49,350
♫ When it's sunny, it's my turn to blow haze away for you ♫

15
00:00:49,350 --> 00:00:52,169
♫ Stop hesitating and wandering ♫

16
00:00:52,169 --> 00:00:53,770
♫ Recover from the pain of past memories ♫

17
00:00:53,770 --> 00:00:56,129
♫ Strike a fairy-tale match now ♫

18
00:00:56,129 --> 00:00:58,569
♫ And ignite the spark ♫

19
00:00:58,569 --> 00:01:01,639
♫ The little prince in my heart ♫

20
00:01:01,639 --> 00:01:06,809
♫ Plants golden wheat ♫

21
00:01:06,809 --> 00:01:10,100
♫ Your smile is like the sunshine ♫

22
00:01:10,100 --> 00:01:15,800
♫ That will be always on my mind ♫

