27
00:01:27,859 --> 00:01:29,669
♫ Recover from the pain of past memories ♫

28
00:01:29,670 --> 00:01:31,939
♫ Strike a fairy-tale match now ♫

29
00:01:31,940 --> 00:01:34,609
♫ And ignite the spark ♫

30
00:01:34,609 --> 00:01:38,919
[Be Loved in House: I Do]

31
00:01:38,920 --> 00:01:43,340
[Episode 10: Tin and Copper]

32
00:01:49,910 --> 00:01:52,109
So you sent Mu Qiu Liang over.

33
00:01:52,110 --> 00:01:55,110
- This piece is very special.
- Answer my question.

34
00:01:55,110 --> 00:01:56,509
Did you name this jewelry piece?

35
00:01:56,509 --> 00:01:58,660
- Yi Zi Tong!
- It's E-Stone.

36
00:01:58,660 --> 00:02:00,660
You used to call me this.

37
00:02:01,920 --> 00:02:03,869
I hired that guy,

38
00:02:03,869 --> 00:02:06,519
just like you get paid by accepting projects.

39
00:02:06,520 --> 00:02:08,849
But if you're interested, I can refer you.

40
00:02:08,849 --> 00:02:10,910
Why did you want to test us?

41
00:02:12,390 --> 00:02:14,650
Did you forget why I came here?

42
00:02:18,830 --> 00:02:20,930
They've been in there for so long.

43
00:02:24,210 --> 00:02:27,549
- They're talking about work.
- This is the longest work talk ever.

44
00:02:27,549 --> 00:02:30,789
The thing is, why did Yi Zi Tong bring the pendant?

45
00:02:30,789 --> 00:02:33,900
What's his relationship with that Mu something?

46
00:02:35,970 --> 00:02:38,909
No wonder the client is so rich.

47
00:02:38,909 --> 00:02:43,160
They have Yuan Shan Group backing them.

48
00:02:43,160 --> 00:02:45,099
I never expected to see someone so important

49
00:02:45,099 --> 00:02:47,639
upon walking into the design studio.

50
00:02:47,639 --> 00:02:49,349
Yuan Shan Group is a big company.

51
00:02:49,349 --> 00:02:52,929
You don't have to test this little design studio of ours in a roundabout way.

52
00:02:52,929 --> 00:02:55,779
As a referrer of this international project,

53
00:02:55,780 --> 00:02:57,889
I'm obliged to confirm in the interests of the group

54
00:02:57,889 --> 00:03:01,019
if Jingcherng Metalwork and Design is capable.

55
00:03:01,019 --> 00:03:04,659
- You can choose another studio.
- You're not honest.

56
00:03:04,660 --> 00:03:06,299
When you heard Yuan Shan Group,

57
00:03:06,299 --> 00:03:09,600
did you never think that I would be involved?

58
00:03:11,750 --> 00:03:13,290
Of course,

59
00:03:13,290 --> 00:03:15,400
I came here for three reasons.

60
00:03:15,400 --> 00:03:18,799
First, I'm not interested in mass-produced products without a distinctive style.

61
00:03:18,799 --> 00:03:21,409
We do also have mass-produced products. Also,

62
00:03:21,410 --> 00:03:24,650
since they're called products, it's quite unlikely to avoid mass production.

63
00:03:24,650 --> 00:03:27,429
Second, Chairman Mai thinks highly of you.

64
00:03:27,429 --> 00:03:29,540
I trust his recommendations.

65
00:03:30,880 --> 00:03:32,840
I can't take all the credit.

66
00:03:34,200 --> 00:03:36,400
This is my third reason.

67
00:03:39,960 --> 00:03:41,610
Because of you.

68
00:03:44,200 --> 00:03:46,839
I know what happened that day.

69
00:03:46,839 --> 00:03:49,270
I also know that you ended up being hospitalized.

70
00:03:52,590 --> 00:03:54,700
Why don't you blame me?

71
00:04:03,970 --> 00:04:05,420
Shi Lei,

72
00:04:05,420 --> 00:04:07,500
why don't you voice your opinion?

73
00:04:07,500 --> 00:04:09,860
He has other things to...

74
00:04:11,340 --> 00:04:13,320
worry about.

75
00:04:13,320 --> 00:04:15,080
What?

76
00:04:18,490 --> 00:04:21,440
I don't know. I'm just guessing.

77
00:04:27,910 --> 00:04:31,019
Did something... happen?

78
00:04:31,020 --> 00:04:33,619
Our director has accepted a new project recently.

79
00:04:33,619 --> 00:04:36,369
The renowned Yuan Shan Group.

80
00:04:36,369 --> 00:04:38,919
It's comparable to Chairman Mai,

81
00:04:38,920 --> 00:04:42,700
- who Shi Lei approached.
- Also, the successor of the group came here in person today.

82
00:04:42,700 --> 00:04:45,599
Jin Yu Zhen was a bit shocked.

83
00:04:45,599 --> 00:04:48,229
I feel like they know each other.

84
00:04:48,229 --> 00:04:51,129
Not surprising. He has an awful lot of connections.

85
00:04:51,129 --> 00:04:53,590
Last time he even made us lose the bet.

86
00:04:59,480 --> 00:05:01,199
We will meet again very soon.

87
00:05:01,199 --> 00:05:03,420
I hope we will be happy working together.

88
00:05:21,610 --> 00:05:22,909
What's going on?

89
00:05:22,909 --> 00:05:24,569
They should've made a deal,

90
00:05:24,569 --> 00:05:27,590
but the atmosphere is a bit...

91
00:05:31,220 --> 00:05:33,729
It's been so long since I last saw you, Jin Yu Zhen.

92
00:05:33,729 --> 00:05:35,980
Or should I call you Real?

93
00:05:44,160 --> 00:05:47,280
[HWC Roasters]

94
00:05:56,350 --> 00:05:58,089
It's my first time coming to my senior schoolmate's shop.

95
00:05:58,089 --> 00:06:00,050
It's quite good.

96
00:06:02,830 --> 00:06:05,509
I'm Yu Zhen's senior schoolmate, not yours.

97
00:06:05,510 --> 00:06:07,410
His senior schoolmate is my senior schoolmate.

98
00:06:07,410 --> 00:06:10,069
Should I call you Shop Manager Yan Zhao Gang instead?

99
00:06:10,070 --> 00:06:11,880
What did you come here for?

100
00:06:11,880 --> 00:06:14,759
I thought you would ask why I showed up.

101
00:06:14,759 --> 00:06:16,459
We aren't very close.

102
00:06:16,459 --> 00:06:20,129
- I don't have to dig into it.
- We met several times,

103
00:06:20,130 --> 00:06:22,179
otherwise, how could you recognize me immediately?

104
00:06:22,179 --> 00:06:25,129
Obviously, you figured out his current situation,

105
00:06:25,130 --> 00:06:26,890
including HWC Roasters.

106
00:06:28,340 --> 00:06:31,019
I came to meet you face-to-face first.

107
00:06:31,020 --> 00:06:32,969
Now that I'm working with Jingcherng Metalwork and Design,

108
00:06:32,969 --> 00:06:35,139
I might show up quite often.

109
00:06:35,140 --> 00:06:37,259
You left without saying a word back then.

110
00:06:37,259 --> 00:06:39,090
Now you just suddenly show up.

111
00:06:39,090 --> 00:06:41,320
Of course, I find it strange.

112
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:44,850
Don't you want to bless us?

113
00:06:48,140 --> 00:06:50,340
I came here to save him.

114
00:06:55,760 --> 00:06:58,230
That person won't be you.

115
00:06:59,189 --> 00:07:01,439
Isn't it because of me

116
00:07:01,440 --> 00:07:03,500
that they have that unreasonable Single Rule?

117
00:07:04,700 --> 00:07:07,730
Do you know why I set the rule?

118
00:07:09,160 --> 00:07:12,970
You can't lose something you never had.

119
00:07:17,000 --> 00:07:18,830
Order your food.

120
00:07:23,630 --> 00:07:26,070
How could he come up with the Single Rule?

121
00:07:26,070 --> 00:07:27,639
Let me resolve this,

122
00:07:27,639 --> 00:07:30,769
which is a good deed to him and his team.

123
00:07:30,770 --> 00:07:32,459
What do you want to do to him again?

124
00:07:32,460 --> 00:07:34,789
Why are you worried? Do I look like a bad person?

125
00:07:34,789 --> 00:07:36,799
He doesn't need you to interfere in his life now.

126
00:07:36,800 --> 00:07:38,789
But Jingcherng Metalwork and Design, which he took over,

127
00:07:38,789 --> 00:07:43,229
really needs Yuan Shan Group's temporary interference so they'll have no more worries.

128
00:07:43,229 --> 00:07:44,659
What do you know?

129
00:07:44,660 --> 00:07:47,130
Then you need to let me know.

130
00:07:52,240 --> 00:07:54,200
You don't want to tell me?

131
00:07:54,200 --> 00:07:56,120
That's fine.

132
00:07:58,630 --> 00:08:01,190
I know everything, anyway.

133
00:08:35,260 --> 00:08:38,780
Are you zoning out? I knew you'd be here.

134
00:08:42,960 --> 00:08:45,210
What's wrong? Why don't you go home?

135
00:08:46,300 --> 00:08:48,599
I'm thinking about things.

136
00:08:48,599 --> 00:08:50,600
You can go home and think about them.

137
00:08:55,540 --> 00:08:59,110
- Wang Jing told me...
- What did he say?

138
00:08:59,930 --> 00:09:01,920
You have something on your mind.

139
00:09:05,690 --> 00:09:07,419
He didn't tell me everything,

140
00:09:07,419 --> 00:09:10,460
but I know why Wang Jing told me that.

141
00:09:19,710 --> 00:09:23,409
Recently, Wang Jing's mind has been in sync with mine.

142
00:09:23,409 --> 00:09:25,659
We found a way to coexist.

143
00:09:25,659 --> 00:09:27,919
Anyway, Jin Yu Zhen can't investigate

144
00:09:27,920 --> 00:09:30,059
everyone's relationship status by himself.

145
00:09:30,059 --> 00:09:33,139
But I really hate it when we have to keep it a secret.

146
00:09:33,139 --> 00:09:35,099
It's so tiring to hide it.

147
00:09:35,099 --> 00:09:36,989
Exactly.

148
00:09:36,989 --> 00:09:39,180
Hiding it...

149
00:09:39,840 --> 00:09:42,380
seems to be exhausting.

150
00:09:42,389 --> 00:09:44,250
When are you going to confess your feelings then?

151
00:09:47,070 --> 00:09:49,179
Why are you talking about this?

152
00:09:49,179 --> 00:09:51,879
You're courageous whatever you do,

153
00:09:51,879 --> 00:09:55,300
but when it comes to relationships,

154
00:09:55,300 --> 00:09:58,500
you'll become like this.

155
00:09:58,500 --> 00:10:00,990
Do you think I don't know you?

156
00:10:00,990 --> 00:10:02,779
If you truly love someone,

157
00:10:02,779 --> 00:10:04,459
gather the courage to confess your feelings.

158
00:10:04,459 --> 00:10:05,769
It's just what I think.

159
00:10:05,769 --> 00:10:07,879
Look at Old Gang and little Qi Qi.

160
00:10:07,880 --> 00:10:09,480
How nice.

161
00:10:10,540 --> 00:10:12,349
Are they that obvious?

162
00:10:12,349 --> 00:10:15,689
Come on! They're so madly in love.

163
00:10:15,689 --> 00:10:19,309
But little Qi Qi isn't worried about getting fired at all.

164
00:10:19,309 --> 00:10:21,760
We all should learn to be courageous like him.

165
00:10:34,100 --> 00:10:36,140
Let's have a toast to courage.

166
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:41,000
You can drink, but don't vomit on me.

167
00:11:06,480 --> 00:11:08,130
Are you awake?

168
00:11:11,230 --> 00:11:13,299
You look quite comfortable.

169
00:11:13,299 --> 00:11:15,190
What did you just dream of?

170
00:11:21,200 --> 00:11:25,440
Have you thought about getting married?

171
00:11:29,620 --> 00:11:32,340
Why do you suddenly ask about this?

172
00:11:33,230 --> 00:11:37,209
Because when Big Bro Lei asked you about the director,

173
00:11:37,209 --> 00:11:40,319
you said you were a wanderer,

174
00:11:40,319 --> 00:11:43,440
and you'd never made whatever you were losing stay.

175
00:11:48,630 --> 00:11:51,470
Have you never thought about settling down?

176
00:11:52,430 --> 00:11:54,899
When I was your age,

177
00:11:54,899 --> 00:11:57,449
society wasn't like what it is now.

178
00:11:57,449 --> 00:12:00,800
That's why I came to terms with reality a long time ago.

179
00:12:02,440 --> 00:12:05,270
Can you be in a serious relationship with me then?

180
00:12:09,690 --> 00:12:11,900
In the moment,

181
00:12:12,910 --> 00:12:14,819
- I'm always very serious.
- I mean,

182
00:12:14,819 --> 00:12:18,120
assuming we won't break up in the future.

183
00:12:19,160 --> 00:12:22,040
Before you reach my age,

184
00:12:22,520 --> 00:12:25,099
you'll still meet many people

185
00:12:25,099 --> 00:12:27,549
and even some who are better than me.

186
00:12:27,549 --> 00:12:30,230
Are you helping me get ready for it?

187
00:12:32,210 --> 00:12:35,570
Maybe... I'm helping myself.

188
00:12:36,039 --> 00:12:38,960
I've constantly been thinking about getting married.

189
00:12:40,560 --> 00:12:41,859
Great then.

190
00:12:41,859 --> 00:12:44,479
It's not great unless I'm with you.

191
00:12:44,479 --> 00:12:46,229
I'm only your first love.

192
00:12:46,229 --> 00:12:48,399
If you were never in a serious relationship before,

193
00:12:48,399 --> 00:12:50,509
then I'm your first love, too.

194
00:12:50,509 --> 00:12:53,090
The really, really serious kind.

195
00:12:58,700 --> 00:13:00,639
You're so talkative today

196
00:13:00,639 --> 00:13:04,030
just because of what I said to Shi Lei?

197
00:13:17,600 --> 00:13:19,210
Si Qi.

198
00:13:21,730 --> 00:13:24,579
I really have a hard time imagining

199
00:13:24,579 --> 00:13:26,930
marrying anyone.

200
00:13:29,190 --> 00:13:31,540
What if

201
00:13:31,540 --> 00:13:33,300
it's me?

202
00:14:05,960 --> 00:14:07,549
Yes.

203
00:14:07,549 --> 00:14:10,710
♫ I do! I do! I do ♫

204
00:14:12,079 --> 00:14:15,570
♫ Because I do! I do! I do ♫

205
00:14:16,930 --> 00:14:19,250
♫ The coffee shop on the street corner ♫

206
00:14:19,250 --> 00:14:21,540
♫ Has the smell of bubbles ♫

207
00:14:21,549 --> 00:14:24,149
♫ I have an indescribable gut feeling ♫

208
00:14:24,149 --> 00:14:26,589
♫ That I may run into someone today ♫

209
00:14:26,589 --> 00:14:28,709
♫ It's finally on the hour ♫

210
00:14:28,709 --> 00:14:31,059
♫ The streets are ablaze with color as usual ♫

211
00:14:31,059 --> 00:14:33,779
♫ Feeling romantic in the breeze alongside the river ♫

212
00:14:33,779 --> 00:14:36,069
♫ I can't help spinning excitedly ♫

213
00:14:36,069 --> 00:14:38,969
♫ The midnight showing got delayed ♫

214
00:14:38,969 --> 00:14:43,219
♫ That day you made a promise ♫

215
00:14:43,219 --> 00:14:45,929
♫ And I wished upon a shooting star ♫

216
00:14:45,929 --> 00:14:52,809
♫ Your face profile, smile and eyes are irresistible ♫

217
00:14:52,809 --> 00:14:56,300
♫ I'm gonna share with you, my love ♫

218
00:15:05,040 --> 00:15:06,980
Are you cooking dinner?

219
00:15:07,829 --> 00:15:10,129
No, I'll do it myself in a bit.

220
00:15:10,129 --> 00:15:11,930
Or do you want to eat with me?

221
00:15:12,530 --> 00:15:13,800
No.

222
00:15:30,600 --> 00:15:33,640
- Are you not done taking a shower?
- Not yet.

223
00:15:35,690 --> 00:15:38,350
- I'll wait for you then.
- I need a lot of time.

224
00:16:19,900 --> 00:16:21,819
Work.

225
00:16:21,819 --> 00:16:25,309
Big Bro Lei, you... are you okay?

226
00:16:25,309 --> 00:16:27,250
- I'm great.
- Nonsense.

227
00:16:29,550 --> 00:16:32,780
So... do you have any ideas?

228
00:16:33,590 --> 00:16:38,019
- After you've archived the files, we'll—
- I'm not talking about the summer projects.

229
00:16:38,019 --> 00:16:41,520
I'm talking about the director's project.

230
00:16:42,219 --> 00:16:43,889
Didn't you know?

231
00:16:43,889 --> 00:16:47,079
Yi Zi Tong, based on the last custom order,

232
00:16:47,079 --> 00:16:50,519
came up with a new theme called "the Only One."

233
00:16:50,519 --> 00:16:53,979
Did the director not mention it to you?

234
00:16:53,979 --> 00:16:56,680
We've all heard about it. Only you didn't know about it?

235
00:16:59,790 --> 00:17:02,969
- Maybe I missed it.
- We don't care if you're absent-minded,

236
00:17:02,969 --> 00:17:05,039
but they didn't discuss it with you, the team leader—

237
00:17:05,039 --> 00:17:07,649
I think the project looks fine.

238
00:17:07,649 --> 00:17:10,670
You just need to adjust some minor details.

239
00:17:20,870 --> 00:17:22,809
I believe we can handle it ourselves.

240
00:17:22,809 --> 00:17:24,230
Let's go.

241
00:17:52,420 --> 00:17:53,740
Wow,

242
00:17:53,740 --> 00:17:56,259
I didn't expect to see Jin Yu Zhen play along.

243
00:17:56,259 --> 00:17:58,659
I told you they must know each other.

244
00:17:58,659 --> 00:18:01,570
Not many people can control our director.

245
00:18:31,240 --> 00:18:36,309
♫ Turning a comma like a kid ♫

246
00:18:36,309 --> 00:18:41,259
♫ Words and expressions run wild, being molded
into the shape of you ♫

247
00:18:41,259 --> 00:18:45,909
♫ I guess I'm still the same ♫

248
00:18:45,909 --> 00:18:52,639
♫ I'm carried away by your confusing grammar ♫

249
00:18:52,639 --> 00:18:57,919
♫ I'm like a rendered portrait ♫

250
00:18:57,919 --> 00:19:03,079
♫ A flower blooms on the right side of my chest at dawn ♫

251
00:19:03,079 --> 00:19:08,079
♫ Nobody wants to write the wrong
time difference in parting ♫

252
00:19:08,079 --> 00:19:10,849
♫ I think for a bit ♫

253
00:19:10,849 --> 00:19:13,279
♫ Then erase the truth ♫

254
00:19:13,279 --> 00:19:17,869
♫ I want to fly into clouds ♫

255
00:19:17,869 --> 00:19:24,429
♫ It's a little complicated but simple for me to be stubborn ♫

256
00:19:24,429 --> 00:19:29,709
♫ The gentle breeze is blowing into your world ♫

257
00:19:29,709 --> 00:19:32,509
♫ Borrowing could be beautiful ♫

258
00:19:32,510 --> 00:19:35,179
♫ There's no comma leading to a sequel ♫

259
00:19:35,179 --> 00:19:37,759
♫ Who gives a nod? ♫

260
00:19:37,759 --> 00:19:40,499
♫ Who gives precedence to that empty seat? ♫

261
00:19:40,499 --> 00:19:45,969
♫ Why do you always apologize to me? Period ♫

262
00:19:45,969 --> 00:19:48,589
♫ The rain is gently dripping ♫

263
00:19:48,589 --> 00:19:51,349
♫ Catching up with the last page ♫

264
00:19:51,349 --> 00:19:56,669
♫ I'm used to wasting what's tasteless as I don't like it ♫

265
00:19:56,669 --> 00:19:59,429
♫ I feel numb walking forward ♫

266
00:19:59,429 --> 00:20:02,849
♫ Honesty comes from guilt ♫

267
00:20:02,849 --> 00:20:05,529
♫ A line separator. In reality ♫

268
00:20:05,530 --> 00:20:11,390
♫ I realize you said it right ♫

269
00:20:33,170 --> 00:20:35,540
So Shi Lei knows everything?

270
00:20:39,040 --> 00:20:40,949
Zi Tong actually came to talk to you.

271
00:20:40,949 --> 00:20:43,179
Shi Lei happened to be here as well.

272
00:20:43,179 --> 00:20:44,979
How come?

273
00:20:44,979 --> 00:20:49,269
Basically, I only heard about what happened between you and Zi Tong

274
00:20:49,269 --> 00:20:52,260
so it's hard for me to give you any suggestions.

275
00:20:54,250 --> 00:20:56,520
Why are you suddenly bringing it up?

276
00:20:57,730 --> 00:21:00,869
Yu Zhen, you know it very well,

277
00:21:00,869 --> 00:21:04,760
but you don't want to or even dare to admit it.

278
00:21:08,580 --> 00:21:12,649
You haven't confessed your feelings for so long that you've lost courage.

279
00:21:12,649 --> 00:21:14,629
I can totally understand it.

280
00:21:14,630 --> 00:21:17,439
But there are things that you can't just ask.

281
00:21:17,439 --> 00:21:20,299
You can't force other people to take the initiative

282
00:21:20,299 --> 00:21:22,710
because you're afraid of getting hurt.

283
00:21:25,160 --> 00:21:27,899
Sorry, I just assumed everything.

284
00:21:27,899 --> 00:21:31,460
Think of it as me talking about someone else.

285
00:21:48,600 --> 00:21:51,560
Shop Manager, is he okay?

286
00:21:55,600 --> 00:21:57,470
A picnic?

287
00:21:59,560 --> 00:22:02,759
Didn't you say that Yu Zhen was nice to keep it a secret for Si Qi?

288
00:22:02,759 --> 00:22:05,809
Consider it my way to show gratitude as his senior schoolmate.

289
00:22:05,810 --> 00:22:07,720
What do you think?

290
00:22:09,390 --> 00:22:11,660
Then I'll let you pass on the message.

291
00:22:13,180 --> 00:22:15,499
Isn't it better for you to say it yourself?

292
00:22:15,499 --> 00:22:17,259
You spend more time with him.

293
00:22:17,259 --> 00:22:19,169
But he's been so busy lately. I don't think he has time for it.

294
00:22:19,170 --> 00:22:22,760
I'm busy, too. Pass it on for me.

295
00:22:23,269 --> 00:22:25,009
I...

296
00:22:25,009 --> 00:22:27,319
Just tell me if you have any difficulties.

297
00:22:27,319 --> 00:22:30,760
Don't mutter. It's not like you.

298
00:22:32,000 --> 00:22:36,029
Or you can give me your address so I can help you pass it on.

299
00:22:37,189 --> 00:22:40,110
Or I'll go straight to the design studio.

300
00:22:41,910 --> 00:22:44,239
Then Jin Yu Zhen will wonder

301
00:22:44,239 --> 00:22:46,989
why it isn't Shi Lei telling him.

302
00:22:46,990 --> 00:22:50,169
Is he that kind of person who purposely asks about reasons?

303
00:22:50,170 --> 00:22:52,740
You need to ask Shi Lei.

304
00:22:55,260 --> 00:22:57,420
I'll tell him personally.

305
00:23:04,240 --> 00:23:05,780
I have to go now.

306
00:23:17,640 --> 00:23:19,110
Gang.

307
00:23:22,700 --> 00:23:25,059
Why do you suddenly call me that?

308
00:23:25,059 --> 00:23:26,779
I just want to try.

309
00:23:26,780 --> 00:23:28,110
Let me ask you something.

310
00:23:28,110 --> 00:23:31,679
Have you found Big Bro Lei and our director weird lately?

311
00:23:31,679 --> 00:23:33,669
Why?

312
00:23:33,670 --> 00:23:35,679
Are they together?

313
00:23:35,679 --> 00:23:39,619
But doesn't the design studio have the Single Rule?

314
00:23:39,619 --> 00:23:41,459
The director can keep it a secret, too.

315
00:23:41,459 --> 00:23:45,629
Whatever. Anyway, they seem to have been avoiding each other lately.

316
00:23:45,629 --> 00:23:48,789
The atmosphere is not the same as it was.

317
00:23:48,789 --> 00:23:52,460
Maybe they're different at home.

318
00:23:53,610 --> 00:23:55,229
Like...

319
00:23:55,229 --> 00:23:57,889
this? Or...

320
00:23:57,889 --> 00:23:59,829
- this?
- It tickles.

321
00:23:59,829 --> 00:24:02,740
Don't tickle me.

322
00:24:02,740 --> 00:24:05,659
♫ It's not too bad without a few perfunctory words ♫

323
00:24:05,660 --> 00:24:07,370
How about this?

324
00:24:07,370 --> 00:24:09,820
♫  Can't do anything about it  ♫

325
00:24:09,830 --> 00:24:12,709
♫ My friends' gathering is a bit of a blast ♫

326
00:24:12,709 --> 00:24:15,489
♫ Sorry, I can't laugh now ♫

327
00:24:15,489 --> 00:24:17,669
♫ I don't have time to spend with you ♫

328
00:24:17,669 --> 00:24:19,439
♫ I want to figure it out ♫

329
00:24:19,439 --> 00:24:21,509
♫ I feel like you're not here again ♫

330
00:24:21,510 --> 00:24:23,959
♫ The awkwardness between people ♫

331
00:24:23,960 --> 00:24:26,039
♫ We walk hand in hand ♫

332
00:24:26,040 --> 00:24:29,429
♫ It feels a little strange when I can't keep up ♫

333
00:24:29,429 --> 00:24:32,739
♫ Don't worry. Baby, you're so fine ♫

334
00:24:32,739 --> 00:24:35,259
♫ I just don't understand it ♫

335
00:24:35,259 --> 00:24:39,389
♫ I want to be impulsive but too afraid of failing ♫

336
00:24:39,389 --> 00:24:42,369
♫ I'm stucking here alone ♫

337
00:24:42,369 --> 00:24:45,699
♫ How much do I like you? ♫

338
00:24:45,699 --> 00:24:48,949
♫ When do we talk about love? ♫

339
00:24:48,949 --> 00:24:52,299
♫ Now we're lying on the roof ♫

340
00:24:52,299 --> 00:24:55,249
♫ Now what you gonna do ♫

341
00:24:55,249 --> 00:24:58,609
♫ Maybe no reasons are needed. I'm just lonely ♫

342
00:24:58,609 --> 00:25:02,909
♫ The awkward conversation turned out to feel warm ♫

343
00:25:08,930 --> 00:25:10,470
Jin Yu Zhen.

344
00:25:12,520 --> 00:25:14,080
What are you...

345
00:25:23,720 --> 00:25:27,240
♫ I do! I do! I do ♫

346
00:25:28,080 --> 00:25:31,770
♫ Because I do! I do! I do ♫

347
00:25:33,150 --> 00:25:35,299
♫ The coffee shop on the street corner ♫

348
00:25:35,299 --> 00:25:37,629
♫ has the smell of bubbles ♫

349
00:25:37,629 --> 00:25:40,279
♫ I have an indescribable gut feeling ♫

350
00:25:40,280 --> 00:25:42,669
♫ that I may run into someone today ♫

351
00:25:42,669 --> 00:25:44,879
♫ It's finally on the hour ♫

352
00:25:44,879 --> 00:25:47,219
♫ The streets are ablaze with color as usual ♫

353
00:25:47,219 --> 00:25:49,829
♫ Feeling romantic in the
breeze alongside the river ♫

354
00:25:49,829 --> 00:25:52,109
♫ I can't help spinning excitedly ♫

355
00:25:52,109 --> 00:25:55,049
♫ The midnight showing got delayed ♫

356
00:25:55,049 --> 00:25:59,179
♫ That day you made a promise ♫

357
00:25:59,179 --> 00:26:01,899
♫ and I wished upon a shooting star ♫

358
00:26:02,000 --> 00:26:08,859
♫ Your face profile, smile and eyes are irresistible ♫

359
00:26:08,859 --> 00:26:11,949
♫ I'm gonna share with you, my love ♫

360
00:26:11,949 --> 00:26:13,739
♫ I do, do, do ♫

361
00:26:13,739 --> 00:26:16,139
♫ We've promised to meet again in early summer ♫

362
00:26:16,139 --> 00:26:18,429
♫ With the wings that brought us together ♫

363
00:26:18,429 --> 00:26:21,819
♫ I'll fly when sunshine comes after rain ♫

364
00:26:21,819 --> 00:26:25,339
♫ I'll hold it in my hand forever, blooming for you ♫

365
00:26:25,339 --> 00:26:28,119
♫ I know. Oh, oh, oh. ♫

366
00:26:28,119 --> 00:26:31,079
I feel that Jin Yu Zhen still cares about you.

367
00:26:31,079 --> 00:26:33,269
That's why I came looking for him.

368
00:26:33,269 --> 00:26:35,380
Do you still love him then?
